HEADWORD: Diatessaron
<hw>Di`a*tes"sa*ron</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., fr.
Gr. <?/ (sc. <?/); <grk>dia`</grk> through + <?/, gen. of <?/ four (sc.
